title: Grateful Dead Live at Hampton Coliseum on 1987-03-24
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Candyman, Minglewood Blues, Loser, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Ramble On Rose, Let It Grow

Set 2

Gimme Some Lovin'-> Black Muddy River, Playin' In The Band-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Space-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Wharf Rat-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text:
Best Terrapin? According to Charlie Miller, as reported on reddit.  A good one! Jerry on fire!

Who's helping on vocals on Gimme Some Lovin'?
